    <item>
      <title>唐纳德·特朗普的竞选搭档不会是马尔科·卢比奥</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/marco-rubio-will-not-be-trump-s-running-mate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，唐纳德·特朗普不会选择佛罗里达州参议员马可·卢比奥作为他的竞选伙伴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/marco-rubio-will-not-be-trump-s-running-mate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:16:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普案的驳回呼应了托马斯大法官的特别检察官观点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-classified-documents-case-dismissal-cites-clarence-thomas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州一名法官下令驳回针对唐纳德·特朗普的机密文件案，并引用了最高法院法官克拉伦斯·托马斯最近发表的意见，对特别顾问任命的合宪性提出了质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-classified-documents-case-dismissal-cites-clarence-thomas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 17:53:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟委员因奥尔班外交问题缺席匈牙利会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/eu-commissioners-to-skip-hungary-s-meetings-over-orban-diplomacy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为抗议欧盟总理维克托·奥尔班（Viktor Orban）对莫斯科和北京的外交访问，欧盟委员会将减少参加欧盟轮值主席国匈牙利计划举行的非正式会议的级别。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/eu-commissioners-to-skip-hungary-s-meetings-over-orban-diplomacy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 17:44:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
